ata-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、華南金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2880:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2880\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2880-TW</a>)、華泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2329:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2329\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2329-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
